						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the <hi rend="italic">nandi-maṇḍapa</hi> of the Śiva shrine.</p>						

						<p>7th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This label inscription can be assigned to the 7th century A.D. on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>It probably refers to the lamp <hi rend="italic">(dīpambu)</hi> set up by Saṁsārabhīta. (<hi rend="italic">cf. G.E. No. 38 of 1939.</hi>)</p>						

